The evidence with the title 'Under Trump, nearly half of Americans would pay no income taxes ... ' says Sep 28, 2015  ... Trump 's proposal says it eliminates tax liability for more than 73 million households and takes nearly 50 % of current filers off the income tax rolls entirely. " if you are single and earn less than $25,000, or married and jointly earn less than $ 50,000 , you will not owe any income tax , " Trump'sproposalstates.
